ตกร","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"จิตแพทย์สืบสาวเบื้องหลังของฆาตกรต่อเนื่องที่ยอมรับสารภาพ หลังจากที่เด็กสาว 9 รายหายตัวไป จนพบเงื่อนงำที่ชวนสงสัยว่าเขาคือคนร้าย หรือเหยื่อในเกมอันตรายที่ซับซ้อนยิ่งกว่า"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"स्टीफन","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"हिन्दी","iso_639_1":"hi","iso_3166_1":"IN","english_name":"Hindi"},{"data":{"title":"Stephen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Một bác sĩ tâm thần điều tra một sát nhân hàng loạt đã tự thú sau khi chín cô gái mất tích, song rốt cuộc phải đặt câu hỏi liệu hắn có tội hay là nạn nhân trong ván cờ đen tối hơn."},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"STEPHEN","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Un psychiatre qui évalue un tueur en série ayant avoué ses crimes démêle un réseau complexe de traumatismes, de tromperies et de manipulations psychologiques, pour finalement se demander si le tueur est vraiment coupable ou s'il n'est qu'une victime supplémentaire dans un jeu plus vaste et plus sombre."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"史提芬的自白","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"一名已认罪的杀人犯正在接受精神科医生的评估，这位精神科医生很快发现自己卷入了一场错综复杂的谜团，一切始于一次评估，最终却引向永恒的黑暗。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"스티븐","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"9명의 여자가 실종된 후 자수한 연쇄 살인범. 그의 정신 감정을 맡게 된 정신과 박사는 조사를 진행하면서 그가 진짜 범인인지, 아니면 더 어두운 게임의 희생자인지 의문을 품게 된다."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"Stephen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Psychiatra oceniający samookreślającego się jako seryjny morderca rozwija skomplikowaną sieć traumy, podstępu i manipulacji psychologicznej — aż zaczyna się zastanawiać, czy morderca jest naprawdę winny, czy może jest tylko kolejną ofiarą w większej, ciemniejszej grze."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Stephen","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Una psiquiatra investiga a un asesino en serie confeso tras la desaparición de nueve niñas, pero termina cuestionándose si es culpable o víctima de un oscuro juego."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Стивен","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Психиатр, осматривающий серийного убийцу, признавшего себя виновным, распутывает сложную паутину травм, обмана и психологических манипуляций - только для того, чтобы задаться вопросом, действительно ли убийца виновен или это просто ещё одна жертва в более масштабной и темной игре."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"ستيفن","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[],"similar_content":[],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt38681567","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":null,"instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148586,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-12-05T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"14"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"IN","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"iso_639_1":"ta","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-12-05T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"U/A 16+"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","release_dates":[{"note":"Netflix","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"202